Library Management System
Problem Statement
Design and implement a basic library management system where members can borrow and return books. The system should maintain information about books, library members, and borrowing records.
Requirements
1. Classes to Implement:

Book:

Properties: id, title, author, genre, isAvailable, publishedYear
Methods: getters/setters, displayInfo()


Library:

Properties: name, address, collection (array/list of books), members (array/list of members)
Methods: addBook(), removeBook(), searchBookByTitle(), searchBookByAuthor(), displayAvailableBooks()


Member:

Properties: id, name, contactInfo, borrowedBooks (array/list)
Methods: borrowBook(), returnBook(), viewBorrowedBooks()
